channel.title: My Third Model it's a "Dean RazorBack" guitar ^^
channel.description:
i finally made my third model, seeing how i love tha guitar, i made a dean razorback model, it took me some timeto do, but i wasn't really rushing x] take a look and tell me how i can improve, and yes, this is really my third model, CREDITS: 90%me for modelling it 10%Dean Razorback, lol
